===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} {{term|camb}}, from {{proto|Germanic|kamboz}}, from {{proto|Indo-European|gombʰos}}.  Cognate with Dutch {{term|kam|lang=nl}}, German {{term|Kamm}}, Swedish {{term|kam|lang=sv}}; compare Ancient Greek {{term|γόμφος||pin|sc=polytonic}}.

